videos.description: Baylor QB Seth Russell throws two touchdown passes, one to TE Sam Tecklenburg and the other to WR KD Cannon as the Bears break open a 24-0 lead over Northwestern State.
videos.headline: Seth Russell, Baylor blow game open early

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Seth Russell, Baylor blow game open early) 2016/09/02 ESHEET

videos.description: Baylor QB Seth Russell throws two passing touchdowns in the second quarter of the Bears' game against Northwestern State, bringing his total to four passing touchdowns in the first half.
videos.headline: Russell's terrific night continues for Baylor

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Russell's terrific night continues for Baylor) 2016/09/02 ESHEET
